      .hpd-recruitment__subsection
        h4.hpd-recruitment__subtitle 【技術系総合職】

        .hpd-recruitment__list
          p.hpd-recruitment__text 1. 優良住宅部品(BL部品)の認定
          p.hpd-recruitment__text 2. 建築確認検査、住宅性能評価
